description:
The Ubuntu Budgie team are pleased to announce our first official beta release for 17.04.

Release notes can be found here (https://wiki.ubuntu.com/ZestyZapus/Beta1/UbuntuBudgie) and if you are interesting in helping us test and find those pesky bugs, look at our testing page for instructions and download links (https://ubuntubudgie.org/17-04-testing)
